Package com.sun.tools.visualvm.core.datasupport

Various helper methods and interfaces for manipulations with DataSources.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    DataChangeListener<X>
    A listener for receiving changes for a monitored data repository.
    DataRemovedListener<X>
    A listener for one-time notifications that the data became finished.
    Positionable
    Common interface for entities that can specify their position within other entities.
    Stateful
    Common interface for entities that can specify their state.

    ClassNameComparator

    WeakReference delegating hashCode() and equals(Object) methods to the referenced object.

    An event containing information about added, removed and actual items of a monitored repository.
    DataChangeSupport<X>
    This is a utility class that can be used by similarly to PropertyChangeSupport.

    Implementation of Comparator based on getPreferredPosition() value.
    Utils
    Utils class encapsulating various helper methods.
